town\n|Hagerstown\n|Hamilton Town\n|Harristown\n|Hartington Town Quarter\n|Heath Town\n|Helltown\n|High Town,Hightown\n|Hilltown\n|Hockeytown\n|Hoskinstown\n|Hopetown,Hope Town\n|Huntingtown\n|Hymietown\n|Irishtown\n|Irvinestown\n|Jamestown\n|Jamisontown\n|Jeffersontown\n|Jenkintown\n|Jeppestown\n|Johnstown\n|Jonestown\n|Jordanstown\n|Kelleytown\n|Kemp Town\n|Kentish Town\n|Kent Town\n|Kingstown\n|Koreatown\n|Kwinana Town Centre\n|Laketown\n|Latte Town\n|Lawrencetown\n|Leonardtown\n|Levittown\n|Lewistown\n|Lombardstown\n|Lordstown\n|Low Town\n|Marshalltown\n|Marystown\n|Marytown\n|Matlock Town\n|Maurertown\n|Medway Towns\n|Middletown\n|Mifflintown\n|Millertown\n|Milltown\n|Mitchellstown,Mitchelstown\n|Mobtown\n|Morgantown\n|Morristown\n|Motown\n|Murray Town\n|Nethertown\n|Newtown,New Town\n|Nicholtown\n|Niggatown\n|Niggertown\n|Norristown\n|Old Town\n|Orangetown\n|Paechtown\n|Pembrey and Burry Port Town\n|Philipstown\n|Pittstown\n|Pitt Town\n|Pitt Town Bottoms\n|Powelltown\n|Princetown\n|Provincetown\n|Puddletown\n|Pumpkintown\n|Queenstown\n|Randalstown\n|Robertstown\n|Rootstown\n|Rosetown\n|Ruyton-XI-Towns\n|Sapphiretown\n|Savile Town\n|Scotchtown\n|Seatown\n|Shortstown\n|Silvertown\n|Simonstown\n|Skellytown\n|Smithtown\n|Smokeytown\n|Snowtown\n|Solomontown\n|Somers Town\n|Southtown\n|South Townsville\n|Spanish Town\n|St John's Town of Dalry\n|Station Town\n|Stephentown\n|Stuart Town\n|Thomastown\n|Tinseltown\n|Town Common\n|Town End,Townend\n|Town Green\n|Town Head,Townhead\n|Town Yetholm\n|Townhill\n|Town Line\n|Townsend\n|Townson\n|Townsville\n|Townsville City\n|Townview\n|Toytown\n|Trench Town\n|Tylertown\n|Uniontown\n|Victoriatown\n|Voluntown\n|Wallacetown\n|Warnertown\n|Watertown\n|West Town\n|Westtown\n|Williamstown\n|Williamstown North\n|Williamtown\n|Wilsontown\n|Wrightstown\n|Yankeetown\n|Yorketown\n|Yorktown,York Town\n|Youngstown\n|Youngtown\n}}\n\n====Descendants====\n* {{desc|ny|tawuni|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|haw|kaona|bor=1}}\n* {{desc|gmw-jdt|tāun|bor=1}}